## рҹҡҰ Ingress / Egress Traffic Control


### Ingress Traffic


```text
  Internet в”Җв”Җв–ә Host:8080 в”Җв”ҖDNATв”Җв”Җв–ә docker0 в”Җв”Җв–ә Container:80

  iptables -A PREROUTING -t nat -p tcp --dport 8080 -j DNAT --to-destination 172.17.0.2:80
  iptables -A FORWARD -p tcp -d 172.17.0.2 --dport 80 -j ACCEPT
```

### Egress Traffic


```text
  Container:80 в”Җв”Җв–ә docker0 в”Җв”ҖMASQUERADEв”Җв”Җв–ә Host:random_port в”Җв”Җв–ә Internet

  iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -s 172.17.0.0/16 ! -o docker0 -j MASQUERADE
```

