## рҹ”җ Docker Secrets Management


```bash
# Swarm mode only for native secrets
echo "db_password_123" | docker secret create db_pass v1

# Mount secret into service
docker service create \
  --secret source=db_pass,target=/run/secrets/db_pass,uid=1000,gid=1000,mode=0400 \
  myapp
```

```yaml
# docker-compose (Swarm mode)
version: "3.9"
services:
  web:
    image: myapp
    secrets:
      - db_pass

secrets:
  db_pass:
    external: true
```

```text
в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
в”Ӯ Manager в”Ӯв”Җв”Җ encrypts secret в”Җв”Җв–ә Raft log (encrypted at rest)
в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ
     в”Ӯ decrypts & mounts on schedule
     в–ј
в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
в”Ӯ Worker  в”Ӯв”Җв”Җ /run/secrets/db_pass (tmpfs, in-memory)
в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ
```

